# S09-T03: Landscape Start & GameOver

## Objective
StartScreen (with mode selector) and GameOverScreen fit 667×375 landscape, CTAs always visible.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Start: title `text-3xl` landscape; mascot `≤80px`; both mode CTAs + melody picker visible above piano fold.
- GameOver: panel `max-h-[90vh] overflow-hidden`, score `text-4xl`, CTA visible.
- Start piano in landscape: hide assistive keyboard OR one-octave compact row.
- No element below `var(--app-height)`.

## Steps
1. Update `StartScreen.tsx` landscape layout (row option: text/CTAs left, mascot right).
2. Update `GameOverScreen.tsx` padding + font clamps.
3. Test 667×375 after S09-T02.
4. `git commit -m "fix(layout): landscape Start and GameOver"`.
